olor: initial;">C&aacute;c nghi&ecirc;n cá»©u chá»‰ ra ráº±ng viá»‡c duy tr&igrave; th&oacute;i quen Ä‘á»c s&aacute;ch, k&iacute;ch th&iacute;ch tr&iacute; n&atilde;o gi&uacute;p l&agrave;m cháº­m qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t triá»ƒn (<em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;">hoáº·c tháº­m ch&iacute; ngÄƒn ngá»«a</em>)&nbsp;bá»‡nh Alzheimer v&agrave; máº¥t tr&iacute; nhá»›. Bá»Ÿi v&igrave; khi giá»¯ cho n&atilde;o cá»§a báº¡n hoáº¡t Ä‘á»™ng li&ecirc;n tá»¥c v&agrave; báº­n rá»™n sáº½ gi&uacute;p ngÄƒn ngá»«a viá»‡c bá»‹ máº¥t nÄƒng lÆ°á»£ng. CÅ©ng giá»‘ng nhÆ° báº¥t ká»³ c&aacute;c cÆ¡ kh&aacute;c trong cÆ¡ thá»ƒ,&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;">n&atilde;o bá»™ cÅ©ng cáº§n Ä‘Æ°á»£c táº­p thá»ƒ dá»¥c Ä‘á»ƒ lu&ocirc;n khá»e máº¡nh</strong>, v&igrave; tháº¿ trong tiáº¿ng Anh c&oacute; cá»¥m tá»« "<em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;">use it or lose it</em>&rdquo; (<em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;">táº¡m dá»‹ch: "Sá»­ dá»¥ng n&oacute; hoáº·c Ä‘&aacute;nh máº¥t n&oacute;"</em>) ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n th&iacute;ch há»£p khi n&oacute;i Ä‘áº¿n n&atilde;o bá»™ cá»§a con ngÆ°á»i. Viá»‡c giáº£i c&aacute;c c&acirc;u Ä‘á»‘ hoáº·c chÆ¡i c&aacute;c tr&ograve; chÆ¡i nhÆ° cá» vua cÅ©ng Ä‘Æ°á»£c cho l&agrave; gi&uacute;p há»¯u &iacute;ch trong viá»‡c&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;">k&iacute;ch th&iacute;ch nháº­n thá»©c</strong>.</p>\r\n<h2 style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 24px; line-height: 34px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">2. Giáº£m cÄƒng tháº³ng</h2>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://i.quantrimang.com/photos/image/2017/07/20/doc-sach-2.jpg" width="456" height="304" /></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Báº¥t ká»ƒ báº£n th&acirc;n báº¡n c&oacute; gáº·p pháº£i bao nhi&ecirc;u cÄƒng tháº³ng tá»« c&ocirc;ng viá»‡c, c&aacute;c má»‘i quan há»‡ c&aacute; nh&acirc;n hay v&ocirc; v&agrave;n c&aacute;c váº¥n Ä‘á» kh&aacute;c pháº£i Ä‘á»‘i máº·t trong cuá»™c sá»‘ng h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y, táº¥t cáº£ sáº½ tan biáº¿n ngay khi báº¡n&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: 